   "source": [
    "# OmniBrain AI/ML Module: VLM & Self-RAG Pipeline (Forced Gemini API)\n",
    "\n",
    "Welcome to the notebook for Project 1: **OmniBrain**. This notebook contains the implementation of Gowtham's AI/ML responsibilities:\n",
    "1. **Vision-Language Model (VLM) Integration** using PyMuPDF and the Google Gemini API.\n",
    "2. **Vision Agent** execution for structured visual extraction (JSON).\n",
    "3. **Self-RAG (Self-Correcting Retrieval-Augmented Generation)** loop using LangGraph."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Step 1: Install Dependencies\n",
    "Run the cell below to install all required libraries in your environment."
   ]
  },
